{% comment %}
  ANVIL — Nav back link snippet
  File: snippets/anvil-nav-back.liquid

  HOW TO INSTALL:
  1. Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → Edit Code
  2. Snippets → Add new snippet → name it: anvil-nav-back
  3. Paste this file
  4. Open Sections → header.liquid (or header-group.liquid in Fluid)
  5. Find the opening <nav> or the first element inside the header
  6. Add this line as the very first child inside the header inner wrapper:
       {% render 'anvil-nav-back' %}
{% endcomment %}

<a href="{{ shop.metafields.anvil.website_url | default: 'https://anvilstudio.co.uk' }}" class="anvil-back-link">
  <span class="anvil-back-link__arrow">←</span>
  <span class="anvil-back-link__label">Go back</span>
</a>
